<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA32">
<l>tamakkaṭimai vēṇṭuvōr tāmō taraṉār</l>
<l>tamakkaṭimai ceyyeṉṟāl ceyyā temakkeṉṟu</l>
<l>tāñceyyun tīviṉaikkē tāḻvuṟuvar neñciṉār</l>
<l>yāñceyva tivviṭattiṅ kiyātu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tāmōtaraṉ is one who wants [people] to be servant to him.</l>
<l>Without doing it when they are told “do servantship to him”, they are people</l>
<l>with hearts that have the degradation of the bad deeds they do, saying “ours”.</l>
<l>What is our doing here in this place?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
